*Gouinia pilosa* (Presl) Scribn. (handwritten)

RANCHO SANTA ANA BOTANIC GARDEN
PLANTS OF MEXICO

Nayarit: Isabel Island, E of Tres Marias Is.
Volcanic islet--cormorant and tern breeding ground.

Porous soil.
